---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Veteran Support Services"
  description="Explore the range of support services available to UK veterans through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme, including mental health, career transition, and housing assistance.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Veteran Support Services</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) is committed to providing comprehensive support to veterans beyond financial compensation. This page outlines the various support services available to help veterans transition to civilian life and manage any service-related challenges.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Mental Health Services</h2>
        <p>We recognise the importance of mental health support for veterans. Our services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to specialised mental health professionals</li>
          <li>PTSD treatment programmes</li>
          <li>Counselling and therapy services</li>
          <li>Peer support groups</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Career Transition Services</h2>
        <p>To support veterans in their transition to civilian careers, we offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Career counselling and guidance</li>
          <li>CV writing and interview skills workshops</li>
          <li>Job placement assistance</li>
          <li>Vocational training programmes</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Housing Assistance</h2>
        <p>We provide support to ensure veterans have access to suitable housing:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information on social housing options</li>
          <li>Assistance with private rental applications</li>
          <li>Support for home adaptations for disabled veterans</li>
          <li>Temporary accommodation for those at risk of homelessness</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Educational Support</h2>
        <p>We offer educational opportunities to help veterans develop new skills:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information on educational entitlements</li>
          <li>Assistance with university and college applications</li>
          <li>Access to vocational courses and apprenticeships</li>
          <li>Funding advice for further education</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For more detailed information on each support service, please visit the specific pages linked in the sidebar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Quick Links</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/support/mental-health" class="text-decoration-none">Mental Health Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/career-transition" class="text-decoration-none">Career Transition</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/housing" class="text-decoration-none">Housing Assistance</a></li>
              <li><a href="/support/education" class="text-decoration-none">Educational Support</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Need Help?</h3>
            <p>Our support team is here to assist you in accessing the services you need.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
